en.title: FE Welcomes QP Wearer, Muay Thai Boxing Champion Narunat!
en.content: FE is proud to present FE's Quantum Pendant to Muay Thai Boxing Champion Narunat after his knockout win in front of 4,000 audiences in Bangkok recently. Presenting the Quantum Pendant was FE's Thai Country Licensee, Don Chan. The fight was broadcast live to 20 million viewers on Thailand's popular Channel 7.
